==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: kalian
<hw>kalian</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A pipe with a long flexible tube
connected to a container where the smoke is cooled by passing through
water. See also <er>hookah</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hookah, hubble-bubble, narghile, water
pipe.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kalif</ent>⟦br⟧
